import React from 'react';
import { View, Card, CardGrid, Panel, PanelHeader } from '@vkontakte/vkui';

function settings() {
    render(
            <View activePanel="card">
  <Panel id="card">
    <PanelHeader>CardGrid</PanelHeader>
    <Group separator="hide">
      <CardGrid>
        <Card size="l">
          <div style={{ height: 96 }} />
        </Card>
        <Card size="m">
          <div style={{ height: 96 }} />
        </Card>
        <Card size="m">
          <div style={{ height: 96 }} />
        </Card>
        <Card size="s">
          <div style={{ height: 96 }} />
        </Card>
        <Card size="s">
          <div style={{ height: 96 }} />
        </Card>
        <Card size="s">
          <div style={{ height: 96 }} />
        </Card>
        <Card size="l">
          <div style={{ height: 96 }} />
        </Card>
      </CardGrid>
    </Group>
  </Panel>
</View>
        )
    
}
export default settings;
